'''辛西婭·昂耶汀馬納蘇·柴納薩奧克武·艾利沃'''（{{lang-en|Cynthia Onyedinmanasu Chinasaokwu Erivo}}，{{IPAc-en|ə|ˈ|r|iː|v|oʊ}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-dDrowuWSI8|title=Cynthia Erivo Explores ASMR|work=W|date=12 October 2018|access-date=2019-04-20}}</ref>；{{bd|1987年|1月8日}}），[[奈及利亞|奈及利亞]]裔英國女演員、歌手與詞曲作者，她得過多個獎項，包括一座[[艾美獎|艾美獎]]、[[東尼獎|東尼獎]]和[[葛萊美獎|葛萊美獎]]，還曾獲得過[[奧斯卡獎|奧斯卡獎]]和[[金球獎|金球獎]]的提名。

艾利沃於2011年參演《{{link-en|秋水伊人|The Umbrellas of Cherbourg}}》的改編舞台劇，開始其演藝生涯，她的首部英國電視劇上是2015年的《{{link-en|口香糖 (電視劇)|Chewing Gum (TV series)|口香糖}}》。艾利沃在2015至2017年間上演的《[[紫色姐妹花|紫色姐妹花]]》[[百老匯劇院|百老匯音樂劇]]的演技獲得認可，並憑此獲得2016年[[東尼獎最佳音樂劇女主角|東尼獎最佳音樂劇女主角]]和{{link-en|葛萊美獎最佳音樂劇專輯|Grammy Award for Best Musical Theater Album}}。艾利沃在2018年開始嘗試參與電影拍攝，包括《[[寡婦_(電影)|寡婦]]》和《[[壞事大飯店|壞事大飯店]]》，其中在《[[哈莉特|哈莉特]]》中飾演[[廢奴主義|廢奴主義]]者[[哈莉特·塔布曼|哈莉特·塔布曼]]的演技更讓她獲得[[奧斯卡最佳女主角獎|奧斯卡最佳女主角獎]]和[[金球獎最佳戲劇類電影女主角|金球獎最佳戲劇類電影女主角]]的提名，她為該片演唱並作詞的主題曲《{{link-en|站起來 (歌曲)|Stand Up (Cynthia Erivo song)|站起來}}》亦獲提名[[奧斯卡最佳原創歌曲獎|奧斯卡最佳原創歌曲獎]]與[[金球獎最佳原創歌曲|最佳原創歌曲]]。

== 生平 ==
=== 早年生活與個人生活 ===
艾利沃於1987年1月8日出生於倫敦南部的[[斯托克韋爾|斯托克韋爾]]，父母皆為[[奈及利亞|奈及利亞]]裔<ref name=autogenerated1>{{cite web|last1=Wolf|first1=Matt|title=A Star Is Born! Meet Cynthia Erivo, Who Plays Celie in John Doyle's London Premiere of The Color Purple|url=http://london.broadway.com/buzz/170679/a-star-is-born-meet-cynthia-erivo-who-plays-celie-in-john-doyles-london-premiere-of-the-color-purple/|website=Theatre.com|access-date=19 June 2016|date=17 July 2013}}</ref>，她的母親是一位護士<ref>{{Cite web | url=https://www.oprahmag.com/entertainment/tv-movies/a28482426/who-is-cynthia-erivo/ |title = Cynthia Erivo Reveals How She Accessed Sadness to Portray Harriet Tubman|work=O, The Oprah Magazine|date = 28 October 2019|access-date=16 August 2020}}</ref>。艾利沃的中學時代就讀於{{link-en|拉雷垂特羅馬天主教女子學校|La Retraite Roman Catholic Girls' School}}，畢業後前往[[東倫敦大學|東倫敦大學]]修讀{{link-en|音樂心理學|Music psychology}}學位<ref name="Guard">{{cite web | url=https://www.theguardian.com/stage/2015/jul/27/cynthia-erivo-the-color-purple-broadway-production | title=Move over Whoopi! How Cynthia Erivo made The Color Purple her own | work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] | date=27 July 2015 | access-date=13 December 2015 | author=John, Emma}}</ref>，但一年後她便轉學至[[皇家戏剧艺术学院|皇家戏剧艺术学院]]<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.whatsonstage.com/london-theatre/news/leading-ladies-cynthia-erivo-henry-iv_36497.html | title=Leading Ladies: Cynthia Erivo 'I want to do everything' | work=What's On Stage | date=19 November 2014 | access-date=13 December 2015 | author=Bosanquet, Theo}}</ref>。

艾利沃是一位[[天主教徒|天主教徒]]<ref>{{cite web|last1=Paulson|first1=Michael|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/12/23/theater/the-actress-cynthia-erivo-rises-with-the-color-purple.html|title=The Actress Cynthia Erivo Rises With 'The Color Purple'|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=22 December 2015|access-date=16 August 2020}}</ref>。她曾與{{link-en|迪安·約翰-威爾森|Dean John-Wilson}}為男女朋友<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-36549967|title=Cynthia Erivo: Tony award win has not sunk in|work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|date=16 June 2016|access-date=16 August 2020}}</ref>。兩人分手後，艾利沃在2017年開始與馬里奧·馬丁尼斯（Mario Martinez）約會<ref>{{cite web |first=Yohana|last=Desta |title=How Cynthia Erivo Found Her Voice |url=https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2019/10/how-cynthia-erivo-found-her-voice |work=[[Vanity_Fair_(magazine)|Vanity Fair]] |date=15 October 2019 |access-date=16 August 2020 }}</ref>。

=== 演藝生涯 ===
==== 音樂劇 ====
[[File:Cynthia_Erivo_2018.png|thumb]]
艾利沃頭幾部參演的電視劇包括《{{link-en|口香糖 (電視劇)|Chewing Gum (TV series)|口香糖}}》和《{{link-en|邊隧謎案|The Tunnel (TV series)}}》，她的第一部舞台劇是由{{link-en|西蒙·史蒂芬斯|Simon Stephens}}所作的《{{link-en|馬林百列大道|Marine Parade (play)}}》<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.thestage.co.uk/features/interviews/2015/big-interview-cynthia-erivo/ | title=Cynthia Erivo: 'You have to drag me off the stage' | work=[[The_Stage|The Stage]] | date=26 July 2015 | access-date=13 December 2015 | author=Hemley, Matthew}}</ref>，而音樂劇首秀則為[[約翰·庫利奇·亞當斯|約翰·庫利奇·亞當斯]]於倫敦[[史特拉福_(倫敦)|史特拉福]]上演的《{{link-en|我看著天花板，然後看見天空|I Was Looking at the Ceiling and Then I Saw the Sky}}》<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theartsdesk.com/opera/i-was-looking-ceiling-and-then-i-saw-sky-theatre-royal-stratford-east|title=I Was Looking at the Ceiling and Then I Saw The Sky, Theatre Royal Stratford East|website=The Arts Desk|access-date=17 September 2018}}</ref>。2013年，艾利沃在[[班克賽德|班克賽德]]公演的《[[紫色姐妹花|紫色姐妹花]]》音樂劇中飾演主角世蘭·哈利斯（Celie Harris），該角色在電影版中由[[琥碧·戈柏|琥碧·戈柏]]演繹<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.theguardian.com/stage/2013/jul/21/color-purple-menier-chocolate-factory | title=The Color Purple – review | work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] | date=20 July 2013 | access-date=13 December 2015 | last=McCrum|first=Robert}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://london.broadway.com/buzz/169866/complete-casting-announced-for-the-color-purple-at-londons-menier-chocolate-factory/ | title=Complete Casting Announced for The Color Purple at London's Menier Chocolate Factory | work=Theatre.com | date=3 June 2013 | access-date=13 December 2015 | last=Gilbert|first=Ryan}}</ref>。她之後在《[[修女也瘋狂|修女也瘋狂]]》歌劇中飾演主角瑪麗·克拉倫斯修女/德勞瑞斯·卡地亞（Sister Mary Clarence/Deloris Van Cartier），再一次扮演原先戈柏由演繹的角色<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.playbill.com/news/article/u.k.-tour-of-sister-act-will-be-led-by-denise-black-michael-starke-and-cynt-180299 | title=U.K. Tour of Sister Act Will Be Led by Denise Black, Michael Starke and Cynthia Erivo | work=Playbill | date=22 June 2011 | access-date=13 December 2015 | last=Shenton|first=Mark}}</ref>。除此之外，她也為美國電影《[[燈光之外|燈光之外]]》錄製〈在你墜落之前翱翔〉（''Fly Before You Fall''）一曲<ref name=autogenerated1 />。

艾利沃在2015年首次在[[百老匯劇院|百老匯]]亮相，在《紫色姐妹花》的美國重製版重新飾演世蘭<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-35069932 | title=The Color Purple: Cynthia Erivo wows critics in Broadway debut | work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] | date=11 December 2015 | access-date=13 December 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.theguardian.com/stage/2015/mar/17/cynthia-erivo-to-join-jennifer-hudson-in-the-color-purple-bernard-b-jacobs-theatre | title=Cynthia Erivo to join Jennifer Hudson in 'The Color Purple'|date=17 March 2015| work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] | agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] }}</ref>，並從同年12月10日開始在[[紐約|紐約]][[曼哈頓中城|曼哈頓中城]]的{{link-en|伯納德·雅各布斯劇院|Bernard B. Jacobs Theatre}}公演<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.playbill.com/news/article/breakout-london-star-cynthia-erivo-wins-plum-lead-in-broadway-color-purple-revival-344234 | title=Breakout London Star Cynthia Erivo Wins Plum Lead in Broadway Color Purple Revival | work=Playbill | date=16 March 2015 | access-date=13 December 2015 | last=Viagas|first=Robert}}</ref>。憑著此部歌劇，她獲得包括[[東尼獎最佳音樂劇女主角|東尼獎最佳音樂劇女主角]]在內的多個獎項。艾利沃還在2016年9月12日的一日限定音樂會中，詮釋由{{link-en|傑森·羅伯特·布朗|Jason Robert Brown}}所作的《{{link-en|最後那五年|The Last Five Years}}》的女主角凱茜·希亞特（Cathy Hiatt），該晚的收入全數捐予反[[槍械暴力|槍械暴力]]組織{{link-en|布雷迪運動|Brady Campaign}}<ref>{{cite web|last=Piepenburg|first=Erik|title=Cynthia Erivo and Joshua Henry to Star in 'Last Five Years' Benefit|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/08/13/theater/cynthia-erivo-and-joshua-henry-to-star-in-last-five-years-benefit.html|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|access-date=13 August 2016|date=11 August 2016}}</ref>。

2017年2月12日，艾利沃與[[約翰傳奇|約翰傳奇]]一起，在[[第59屆葛萊美獎|第59屆葛萊美獎]]頒獎典禮的緬懷環節上演唱[[海灘男孩|海灘男孩]]的〈{{link-en|只有上帝知道|God Only Knows}}〉<ref>{{cite web|url=http://people.com/music/grammys-2017-john-legend-cynthia-erivo-in-memorium-performance//|title=John Legend and Cynthia Erivo Honor Those We've Lost at Grammys|first=Eric|last=Brown|date=12 February 2017|work=[[People_(magazine)|People]]|access-date=23 February 2017}}</ref>。隔月，她與《紫色姐妹花》的演員們一起，憑著在2016年6月《[[今日秀|今日秀]]》上的表演獲得[[日間艾美獎|日間艾美獎]]的提名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.playbill.com/article/the-color-purple-performance-on-the-today-show-led-by-cynthia-erivo-receives-daytime-emmy-nomination|title=The Color Purple Performance on The Today Show Led By Cynthia Erivo Receives Daytime Emmy Nomination|first=Ryan|last=McPhee|date=23 March 2017|work=Playbill|access-date=25 March 2017}}</ref>，並最終獲獎。2017年11月，艾利沃出現在由[[喬恩·史都華|喬恩·史都華]]主持的慈善節目《{{link-en|眾星之夜|Night of Too Many Stars}}》上，與{{link-en|奎斯特拉夫|Questlove}}和{{link-en|紮根樂團|The Roots}}等人一起演唱[[安德拉·戴|安德拉·戴]]的名曲《{{link-en|崛起 (安德拉·戴歌曲)|Rise Up (Andra Day song)|崛起}}》<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.vulture.com/2017/11/hbo-night-of-too-many-stars-highs-and-lows.html|title=The Highs and Lows of ''Night of Too Many Stars'', Jon Stewart's Autism Benefit Show|website=Vulture|first=Katla|last=McGlynn|date=19 November 2017|access-date=7 October 2019}}</ref>。

==== 電影與電視劇 ====
艾利沃在2018年首次於大銀幕上亮相，於[[新黑色|新黑色]]電影《[[壞事大飯店|壞事大飯店]]》飾演達琳·斯威特（Darlene Sweet）<ref>{{cite web|last1=Marotta|first1=Jenna|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/dakota-johnson-jeff-bridges-jon-hamm-debut-bad-times-at-el-royale-1146306|title='Bad Times at El Royale' Debut Draws Dakota Johnson, Jeff Bridges, Jon Hamm|website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=24 September 2018|access-date=16 August 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Chang|first1=Justin|author-link=Justin Chang|url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-bad-times-at-the-el-royale-review-20181010-story.html|title=Review: Twisty motel noir 'Bad Times at the El Royale' nearly overstays its welcome|work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|date=10 October 2018|access-date=16 August 2020}}</ref>。同年，她還出演了{{link-en|搶劫電影|Heist film|搶劫}}[[驚悚片|驚悚片]]《[[寡婦_(電影)|寡婦]]》，也是其拍攝的第一部電影<ref>{{cite web|last1=Jones|first1=Nate|url=https://www.vulture.com/2019/10/cynthia-erivo-answers-every-question-we-have-about-widows.html|title=Cynthia Erivo Answers Every Question We Have About 'Widows'|website=[[紐約_(雜誌)|Vulture]]|date=30 October 2019|access-date=16 August 2020}}</ref>。《[[大西洋_(雜誌)|大西洋]]》的戴維·西姆斯（David Sims）在其對《寡婦》的評論中特別提到艾利沃，讚揚她在角色的戲劇性轉變方面做出令人難以置信的表演<ref>{{cite web|last1=Sims|first1=David|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2018/11/widows-steve-mcqueen-viola-davis-review/575908/|title='Widows': Viola Davis Steals McQueen's Heist Thriller|work=[[The_Atlantic|The Atlantic]]|date=15 November 2018|access-date=16 August 2020}}</ref>。

艾利沃之後在《[[哈莉特|哈莉特]]》中飾演主角[[哈莉特·塔布曼|哈莉特·塔布曼]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.playbill.com/article/cynthia-erivo-will-play-harriet-tubman-in-new-film-harriet|title=Cynthia Erivo Will Play Harriet Tubman in New Film Harriet|first1=Andrew|last1=Gans|work=Playbill|date=8 February 2017|access-date=16 August 2020}}</ref><ref name="Harriet">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2017/02/cynthia-erivo-harriet-tubman-macro-movie-1201904555/|title=Cynthia Erivo To Star As Harriet Tubman In Upcoming 'Harriet' Biopic|first=Amanda|last=N'Duka|date=8 February 2017|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|access-date=8 February 2017}}</ref>，該作在2018年10月開始製作<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2018/09/cynthia-erivo-harriet-harriet-tubman-movie-focus-features-1202464257/|title=Focus Features Moving Forward With Harriet Tubman Pic Starring Cynthia Erivo|first1=Anthony|last1=D'Alessandro|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=13 September 2018|access-date=16 August 2020}}</ref>，並在三個月後完成拍攝，於2019年11月1日上映<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.insightnews.com/aesthetics/new-film-honors-the-life-of-harriet-tubman/article_f508d0ea-1aaa-11e9-8e61-cb78db21c579.html|title=New film honors the life of Harriet Tubman |first=Stacy M. |last=Brown|website=Insight News|access-date=28 January 2019}}</ref>。她的表演使她獲得[[金球獎最佳戲劇類電影女主角|金球獎最佳戲劇類電影女主角]]的提名<ref>{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2019/film/news/2020-golden-globes-nominations-list-nominees-1203426905/|title=Golden Globes 2020: The Complete Nominations List|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=9 December 2019|access-date=9 December 2019}}</ref>；此外還因其在《{{link-en|站起來 (歌曲)|Stand Up (Cynthia Erivo song)|站起來}}》的作詞和主唱工作獲提名[[金球獎最佳原創歌曲|最佳原創歌曲]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/12/cynthia-erivo-harriet-golden-globe-nominations-reaction-1202804912/|title='Harriet' Star Cynthia Erivo Lands Double Golden Globe Nominations, Talks Harriet Tubman & Aretha Franklin|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=9 December 2019|last=N'Duka|first=Amanda|access-date=16 August 2020}}</ref>。2020年，艾利沃獲得[[奧斯卡最佳女主角獎|奧斯卡最佳女主角獎]]和[[奧斯卡最佳原創歌曲獎|最佳原創歌曲獎]]的提名<ref name="Oscar">{{cite web|url=https://www.vox.com/culture/2020/1/13/21060660/oscar-nominees-2020-full-list|last1=Abad-Santos|first1=Alex|last2=Wilkinson|first2=Alissa|website=[[Vox|Vox]]|date=13 January 2020|title=Oscars 2020: the full list of nominees|access-date=16 August 2020}}</ref>。

2020年，艾利沃在[[HBO|HBO]]根據[[史蒂芬·金|史蒂芬·金]]的《{{le|局外人 (小說)|The Outsider (King novel)|局外人}}》改編的[[迷你影集|迷你影集]]《[[異鄉客|異鄉客]]》中飾演調查員{{link-en|霍莉·吉布尼|Holly Gibney}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/01/the-outsider-cynthia-erivo-bill-camp-mare-winningham-paddy-considine-julianne-nicholson-cast-hbo-drama-series-1202541878/|title='The Outsider': Cynthia Erivo, Bill Camp, Mare Winningham, Paddy Considine, Julianne Nicholson Among 10 Cast In HBO Drama Series|last=Petski|first=Denise|date=25 January 2019|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|access-date=28 January 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/01/the-outsider-jason-bateman-richard-price-ben-mendolsohn-cynthia-erivo-hbo-tca-1202831375/|title='The Outsider's Cynthia Erivo Responds To Stephen King's Diversity Comments; Bateman And Price Talk Challenges Adapting Horror Author's Work – TCA|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=15 January 2020|last=Ramos|first=Dino-Ray|access-date=16 August 2020}}</ref>。同年，她創辦了一家名叫「伊迪絲的女兒」（Edith's Daughter）的製作公司，並與媒體公司{{link-en|MRC (公司)|MRC (company)|MRC}}簽訂了通過該公司製作電視節目的協議<ref>{{Cite web|last1=Goldberg|first1=Lesley|title=Cynthia Erivo Inks First-Look Deal With MRC TV, Civic Center Media|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cynthia-erivo-inks-first-look-deal-with-mrc-tv-civic-center-media|date=25 August 2020|access-date=26 August 2020|website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Petski|first1=Denise|url=https://deadline.com/2020/08/cynthia-erivo-first-look-deal-mrc-television-civic-center-media-launches-production-company-1203022253/|title=Cynthia Erivo Inks First-Look Deal With MRC Television & Civic Center Media, Launches Production Company|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=25 August 2020|access-date=26 August 2020}}</ref>。艾利沃還將在《[[世紀天才|世紀天才]]》第三季中飾演[[艾瑞莎·弗蘭克林|艾瑞莎·弗蘭克林]]<ref>{{cite web|last1=Cohn|first1=Gabe|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/02/09/movies/cynthia-erivo-aretha-franklin-trailer.html|title='Genius' Trailer: Cynthia Erivo Plays Aretha Franklin|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=9 February 2020|access-date=26 August 2020}}</ref>，此外她也有參演將於2021年3月5日上映的電影《[[噪反_(電影)|噪反]]》<ref>{{cite web|last1=D'Alessandro|first1=Anthony|url=https://deadline.com/2020/02/chaos-walking-daisy-ridley-tom-holland-january-2021-release-1202854439/|title='Chaos Walking': Daisy Ridley-Tom Holland Pic Gets Release Date|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=7 February 2020|access-date=26 August 2020}}</ref>。與此同時，艾利沃有份獻聲並製作的廣播劇《帶菌者》（''Carrier''）亦確定將登上大銀幕，她本人會飾演其在原作中配音的芮琳·沃特茲（Raylene Watts）一角<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2020/film/news/cynthia-erivo-movie-podcast-carrier-1203502051/|title=Cynthia Erivo to Star in Film Adaptation of Her Podcast 'Carrier'|last=McNary|first=Dave|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=12 February 2020|access-date=22 May 2020}}</ref>。

==== 廣播劇 ====
2019年，艾利沃擔任科幻恐怖廣播劇《帶菌者》的監製，並為作中運送帶有「令人不安的神秘物品」的長途卡車司機，女主角芮琳·沃特茲獻聲<ref>{{cite web |last=Wiseman |first=Andreas |title='Carrier' Podcast First Trailer: Upcoming Thriller Stars 'Bad Times At The El Royale's Cynthia Erivo |url=https://deadline.com/2019/07/carrier-podcast-trailer-cynthia-erivo-qcode-video-1202643823/ |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |access-date=22 May 2020 |date=9 July 2019 }}</ref>。

